text: Duflos is a French surname. Notable people with this surname include: * Adolph Ferdinand Duflos (1802–1889), French pharmacist * Claude Duflos (1665–1727), French engraver * Huguette Duflos (1887–1982), French actress * Patrick Duflos (born 1965), French volleyball player ==See also== * Duflo * Duflot
